{
  "text": "Spectral analysis was performed on Fz using the MATLAB (R2016b, MathWorks, Natick, MA, USA) wavelet coherence package [CITATION_1] , for each peak-to-peak voltage and each frequency value in the range between 200 Hz and 700 Hz, with 25 Hz steps and 50 Hz steps (see Section 3.3).",
